rgin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;\">TS. Phạm Thế Hải&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; width: 206px; height: 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;\">Khoa Sinh học</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; width: 85px; height: 1px;\"><ol style=\"margin: 10px 30px; padding: 0px;\"><li value=\"5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</li></ol></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; width: 263px; height: 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;\">Công nghệ sản xuất chế phẩm vi sinh TBP-Combo phòng trừ vi nấm và tuyến trùng gây hại cây trồng</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; width: 171px; height: 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;\">TS. Trần Văn Tuấn&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; width: 206px; height: 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-